== Tadmsa ==<!-- ad ur tsnflm aḍṛiṣ ad ati druɣ srs ɣ yat tsmɣurt, tanmmirt -->
[[afaylu:Presse olive Volubilis.jpg|gauche|220px|thumb|Azrg n uzatim (lmɛṣṣṛt n zzit)]]
Tettuṣka tmdint n Walili ɣ yan udɣar yẓn i izaɣarn fulkinin d isiffn n Xuman d Fṛṭasa, aylli as ifkan yan waddur yattuyn ɣ yigr n tkrza zɣ izmaz iqburn, zɣ imɣan lli mu ittyafa latṛ nnsn ɣ Walili, llant [[Tumẓin|tmẓin]], [[Ibawn]], [[Tilintit]], [[Aḍil]] d [[Tazart]], ttyafan gis ula 57 n uzrg n uzatim (lmɛṣṣṛt n zzit).<ref name="megalithic">[https://m.megalithic.co.uk/article.php?sid=14906 Volubilis - Ancient Village or Settlement in Morocco]</ref> Ɣ uzmz n tnbaḍt n Iṛumiyn ar tssfuɣ Walili [[Azatim]] (zzit) d imudar gʷrdnin ula wid ḍuẓnin, zun d ifasiwn lli smaɣn Iṛumiyn d ismgan ar tn ttḍufn.<ref name="megalithic"/>

== Tuṣkiwt tamazdart ==<!-- ad ur tsnflm aḍṛiṣ ad ati druɣ srs ɣ yat tsmɣurt, tanmmirt -->
Ɣ uzmz n Iṛumiyn tbuɣla tmsdagt d lbni ɣ Walili s tɣarast taṛumiyt, tusɛu gis tmdint kigan, tugtt n tuṣkiwin ttuṣkant s yan wanaw n uẓṛu ar t id qqazn ɣ udranr n Ẓṛhun, iga uklu nns amiɣid yaẓ nn s ujnjaṛiy. Tettyawssan Walili s tugtt n fusayfisa ɣ ttuṛcamn imudar d imɣan lli gis llanin ɣ uzmz ann, ula wid ganin ɣar ummiyn.<ref name="n836">[https://whc.unesco.org/document/154403 UNESCO], World Heritage List, Volubilis, Morocco, N 836.</ref>

