== Irzzutn irkyulujitn ==<!-- ad ur tsnflm aḍṛiṣ ad ati druɣ srs ɣ yat tsmɣurt, tanmmirt -->
[[Afaylu:Volubilis Decauville track.jpg|220px|gauche|thumb]]
Irzzutn ggutnin ɣ Walili ttuskarn ɣ uzmz n usdurry afṛaniṣ gr isggʷasn 1912 d 1955, macc ssntan dat n uzmz ad s tmrawin n isggʷasn. zɣ mad tsdurry [[Fṛanṣa]] [[Dzayr]] ɣ usggʷ 1930, ssntan imassan irkyulujitn ifṛanṣiṣn irzzutn ɣ idrizn n iṛumiyn llanin ɣ iẓẓlmḍ n tagut d tuẓẓumt n [[Tafriqt|Tfriqt]] s tiḍaf n isrdasn n fṛanṣa.<ref name="Raven">Raven, Susan (1993). Rome in Africa. London: Routledge. ISBN 978-0-415-08150-4.</ref> 

Irzzutn irkyulujitn iskr tn umrzu afṛanṣiṣ [[Hinri du la Martini]] gr isggʷasn 1887 d 1892<ref name="yunisku97">UNESCO Advisory Body Evaluation (PDF). September 1997.</ref> ɣ usggʷs n 1915 ismagl [[Ubir Lyuṭi]], anbbaḍ amsrdas n Lmɣrib ɣ uzmz n usdurry, amrzu aṛkyuluji afṛanṣiṣ  [[Marsil Ugist Dyulafwa]] ([[:en:Marcel-Auguste Dieulafoy|en]]) ad iskar irzzutn ɣ udɣar n walili, dffir as iswuri gis [[Lwis Catilan]] ([[:en:Louis Chatelain|en]]).<ref name="yunisku97"/> Alliɣ yumẓ [[lmɣrib]] azarug nns, smdn isnubbucn ɣ udɣar n Walili ddu tnbaḍt n lmɣtib. 

== Azmem ɣ Yunisku ==<!-- ad ur tsnflm aḍṛiṣ ad ati druɣ srs ɣ yat tsmɣurt, tanmmirt -->
Tskchim [[Yunisku]] adɣar n Walili i tlgamt n idɣarn n taysi tamaḍlant ɣ usggʷas 1997. Ɣ isggʷsn n id 80, iskr [[Asqqim agraɣlan n idrizn d idɣarn|usqqim agraɣlan n idrizn d idɣarn]] ([[:en:International Council on Monuments and Sites|ICOMOS]]) kṛaḍt tinawin d inmuqqarn f idɣarn lli isẓḍaṛ ad kcimn s tlgamt n taysi tamaḍlqnt ɣ iẓẓlmḍ n [[Tafriqt|Tfriqt]], ismagl ilmma usqsim ad ɣ usggʷas 1997 bac ad tkcim Walili s tlgamt n taysi tamaḍlant acku iga yan udɣar ittufragn, iḥḍu timitar n tbɣurt n [[Iṛuminyn]],<ref name="yunisku97"/> tqbl t ilma [[Yunisku|Yunisku]] tsskcim t s tlgamt nns n taysi tamaḍlant.

